# Proviso Review

> Proviso Review is legal bill review software for businesses without an in-house legal department. Upload a law firm invoice and it flags block billing, vague narratives, above-market rates, duplicate entries, and billing-guideline violations — then generates a plain-language report and a ready-to-send reduction request. The first audit is free, with no signup required.

Proviso Review is built for the people who pay outside counsel but have no in-house lawyers to check the bills: business owners, founders, fractional general counsel, and nonprofits. Pricing is flat and published, with no "contact sales" required: Starter is $79 one-time (10 invoices, valid one year), Business is $199/month (25 invoices/month), and Firm is $699/month (100 invoices/month). Verified 501(c)(3) nonprofits receive 25% off any tier.

